                <h1>Fixing Wrong Employment Dates in Background Checks</h1>
                <p>When background checks reveal incorrect employment dates, it can impact job opportunities and credibility. Errors may arise from outdated records or miscommunication. Candidates can address this by verifying their work history with past employers and correcting inaccuracies promptly to prevent potential disputes during hiring processes.</p>
